Package: loadinstall
Title: Loads A Package Or Installs It If Not Available
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("FlÃ¡via", "E. Rius", , "flaviaerius@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-5946-1165"))
Description: {loadinstall} is a simple package to ease the reproducibility of Rmd and qmd scripts. IT has functions to load a package or install it when not available at the same time. You do not need to worry about whether you have or not a library available, for example, when you are running it in a new computer/environment.
